There will be three intercom units, one on each floor of the house(A on the 2nd Floor, B on the 1st Floor
, and C in the Basement)

Here is the Addressing Plan (Pipe 2 is an extra pipe):
|------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|            | Unit A           |     Unit B       |       Unit C        |
|------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|Pipe 0 (RX) | 0xE7D3F03577     | 0x89B4852D52     | 0x771D9E6F77        |
|------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|Pipe 1 (RX) | 0xA6C0A956C6     | 0x6D025403EB     | 0xF62481D485        |
|------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|Pipe 2 (RX) | 0xA6C0A95667     | 0x6D025403D1     | 0xF62481D401        |                 
